- pip install -r requirements.txt
- run file main.py 
- test recognized face -> face_recognition.py
- test detected motion -> motion.py or motion_detection.py
- run set_data.py -> set new preprocess data to train
- run train_model.py -> train model from dataset 
data motion save in dir "./dataset/data_motion"
data train face in dir "./dataset/training_set " and "./dataset/test_set"